== 製作 ==

=== 發展 ===
漫威漫畫作家及編劇{{link-en|格里·康威|Gerry Conway}}和{{link-en|羅伊·托馬斯|Roy Thomas}}在1984年撰寫了一本關於X戰警的劇本，當時Orion Pictures持有電影的版權，但在Orion開始面臨財政危機時，發展便停滯不前。而在1989年和1990年期間，[[史丹·李|史丹·李]]和{{link-en|克里斯·克萊爾蒙特|Chris Claremont}}正在與Carolco Pictures商討一部X戰警改編的電影<ref name="Origin"/>，由[[凱薩琳·畢格羅|凱薩琳·畢格羅]]執導且編劇，[[詹姆斯·卡麥隆|詹姆斯·卡麥隆]]製片，[[金鋼狼|金鋼狼]]角色一任為[[鮑勃·霍斯金斯|鮑勃·霍斯金斯]]所擔任，[[暴風女|暴風女]]則由[[安吉拉·巴塞特|安吉拉·巴塞特]]飾演。但史丹·李的蜘蛛人電影企劃激起了卡麥隆的好奇心，《X戰警》於是不了了之<ref>{{cite news|author=Tim Molloy|url=http://www.thewrap.com/movies/article/chris-claremonts-dream-x-men-movie-james-cameron-kathryn-bigelow-and-bob-hoskins-wolverine-3/?page=0,0|title=Chris Claremont's Dream X-Men Movie: James Cameron, Kathryn Bigelow, and Bob Hoskins as Wolverine|publisher={{link-en|TheWrap.com|TheWrap.com}}|date=2012-03-25|accessdate=2014-10-11|archivedate=2016-03-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309121554/http://www.thewrap.com/chris-claremonts-dream-x-men-movie-james-cameron-kathryn-bigelow-and-bob-hoskins-wolverine-3/|deadurl=no}}</ref>。而後，Carolco破產，電影版權回到了漫威手中<ref name="Origin"/>。1992年12月，漫威討論將版權賣給[[哥倫比亞電影公司|哥倫比亞電影公司]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR101955 | title = Marvel characters holding attraction for filmmakers | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1992-12-09 | accessdate = 2008-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110514215311/http://www.variety.com/article/VR101955 | archive-date = 2011-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，同時{{link-en|艾維·亞拉|Avi Arad}}為[[Fox_Kids|Fox Kids]]製作了動畫連續劇《{{link-en|X戰警（連續劇）|X-Men (TV series)|X戰警}}》，[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]對電視節目的成功印象深刻。1994年，{{link-en|羅倫·舒勒·唐納|Lauren Shuler Donner}}買下了電影版權<ref name="Origin"/><ref name="gen">{{cite news | author = Jeff Jensen | title = Generating ''X'' | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2000-07-21 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,276737,00.html | accessdate = 2008-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150505040519/http://ew.com/article/2000/07/21/x-men-0 | archive-date = 2015-05-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，且讓[[安德鲁·凯文·沃克|安德魯·凱文·沃克]]撰寫該部劇本<ref>{{cite news | author = Steve Daly | title = Deadly Done Right | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 1995-09-29 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,298924,00.html | accessdate = 2007-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071013235845/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,298924,00.html | archive-date = 2007-10-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

沃克的劇本提到[[X教授|X教授]]招募金鋼狼加入X戰警，包含[[獨眼龍_(漫威漫畫)|獨眼龍]]、[[琴葛雷|琴葛雷]]、[[冰人_(漫威漫畫)|冰人]]、[[野獸_(漫畫)|野獸]]和{{link-en|天使（漫威漫畫）|Warren Worthington III|天使}}。{{link-en|變種人聯盟|Brotherhood of Mutants}}（Brotherhood of Mutants）則由[[萬磁王|萬磁王]]、[[劍齒虎_(漫威漫畫)|劍齒虎]]、{{link-en|癩蛤蟆（漫威漫畫）|Doug Sweetland|癩蛤蟆}}、{{link-en|紅坦克（漫威漫畫）|Juggernaut (comics)|紅坦克}}及{{link-en|大塊頭（漫威漫畫）|Blob (comics)|大塊頭}}組成，試圖征服紐約市。而{{link-en|亨利·彼得·傑瑞奇|Henry Peter Gyrich}}和{{link-en|玻利瓦爾·史崔克|Bolivar Trask}}用三個8英尺（2.4米）高的哨兵攻擊X戰警。劇情集中在金鋼狼與獨眼龍間的對抗，以及後者做為領導者的自我懷疑。沃克在1994年6月提交了第二份劇本。之後，{{link-en|雷塔·卡勒葛迪斯|Laeta Kalogridis}}（Laeta Kalogridis）<ref>{{cite journal | first=Stephen | last=Galloway |author2=Donna Parker  | title=4 top ICM agents walk, undertake own Endeavor | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | publisher=[[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen Company]] | date=1995-03-30 }}</ref>、{{link-en|約翰·洛根|John Logan (writer)}}（John Logan）、[[詹姆士·夏姆斯|詹姆士·夏姆斯]]（James Schamus）<ref name="hughes">{{cite book | last = Hughes | first = David | title = Comic Book Movies | publisher = {{link-en|Virgin Books|Virgin Books}} | year = 2003 | pages = 177–188 | isbn = 0-7535-0767-6}}</ref>及[[喬斯·溫登|喬斯·溫登]]重新撰寫了劇本，其中一個段落保留了萬磁王將曼哈頓變成“突變家園”的想法，以及金鋼狼與風暴女之間的情愫<ref name="gen" />。溫登的草稿以{{link-en|訓練室（X戰警）|Danger Room|訓練室}}（Danger Room）及琴葛雷蛻變成為火鳳凰為特色<ref name="Whedon-infocus">{{cite web |url=http://www.natoonline.org/infocus/05augustseptember/whedonuncut.htm |title=In Focus | August/September 2005 | Serenity Now! Uncut |publisher=Natoonline.org |date= |accessdate=2008-10-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615162238/http://www.natoonline.org/infocus/05augustseptember/whedonuncut.htm |archivedate=2011-06-15 }}</ref>。根據《娛樂周刊》，這個劇本最後被退回<ref name="out">{{cite news | author = Craig Seymour | title = X-Man Out | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2000-05-10 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,85186,00.html | accessdate = 2007-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170203200300/http://ew.com/article/2000/05/10/buffy-creator-slams-x-men-movie/ | archive-date = 2017-02-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

福斯原本認定[[布萊特·拉特納|布萊特·拉特納]]擔任其導演<ref>{{cite news|author=Michael Fleming|url=http://variety.com/2005/film/news/new-master-for-mutants-1117923934/|title=New master for mutants|work=Variety|date=2005-06-05|accessdate=2014-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219132908/http://variety.com/2005/film/news/new-master-for-mutants-1117923934/|archive-date=2014-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並提供職位給[[羅伯特·羅德里格斯|羅伯特·羅德里格斯]]，卻遭到拒絕<ref>{{cite news| title = The Total Film Interview-Robert Rodriguez | publisher={{link-en|Total Film|Total Film}} | url = http://www.totalfilm.com/features/robert-rodriguez-interview| date=2003-10-01| accessdate=2007-10-07}}</ref>。繼《[[刺激驚爆點|刺激驚爆點]]》上映後，[[布萊恩·辛格|布萊恩·辛格]]正在尋找一部科幻電影，福斯為他提供了《[[異形4：浴火重生|異形4：浴火重生]]》的執導權，但製片人{{link-en|湯姆·迪桑圖|Tom DeSanto}}認為他會更適合這部電影。到了1996年12月，辛格接下了導演的職務，並於1997年4月聘請了{{link-en|艾迪·所羅門|Ed Solomon}}來撰寫劇本。福斯宣布1998年聖誕節發布日期<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117434784 | title = A Mania For Marvel | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1997-04-14 | accessdate = 2008-03-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110514222636/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117434784 | archive-date = 2011-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Anita M. Busch | url = http://www.variety.com/vstory/VR1117466461.html | title = Singer set to direct Fox's ''Men'' | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1996-12-10 | accessdate = 2008-03-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080919104834/http://www.variety.com/vstory/VR1117466461.html | archive-date = 2008-09-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
電影原定於1999年年中開拍<ref>{{cite news | author = Chris Petrikin | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117491127.html | title = Marvel, Fox pact for pix | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1999-02-09 | accessdate = 2008-03-25}}</ref>，發布日期訂為2000年的聖誕節。但福斯將《X戰警》的發行提前至了6月。[[史蒂芬·史匹柏|史蒂芬·史匹柏]]被安排於2000年6月發表《[[關鍵報告_(電影)|關鍵報告]]》，但史匹柏選擇了拍攝《[[A.I.人工智慧|A.I.人工智慧]]》，福斯需要一部電影填補空缺<ref>{{cite news | author = Chris Petrikin | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117750560.html | title = Fox shifts actioner ''X-Men'' to June | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1999-08-19 | accessdate = 2008-03-25}}</ref>，這意味著辛格不得不提前6個月完成《X戰警》。發布日期最後移至7月14日<ref>{{cite news | author = Chris Petrikin | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117755724 | title = Fox shuffles ''X-Men'' and ''Anna'' | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1999-09-16 | accessdate = 2008-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107123958/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117755724 | archive-date = 2012-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

拍攝於1999年9月22日至2000年3月3日在[[多倫多|多倫多]]和[[安大略省哈密尔顿市|安大略省漢密爾頓]]進行<ref>{{cite web | author = {{link-en|Greg Dean Schmitz|Greg Dean Schmitz}} | title = Greg's Preview - X-Men | publisher = [[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]] | url = http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808406650 | accessdate = 2008-08-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070821124442/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808406650 | archivedate = 2007-08-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=hamfilmA/>，地點包括{{link-en|中央商務大學|Central Toronto Academy}}、{{link-en|釀酒廠區|Distillery District}}及{{link-en|加拿大戰機遺產博物館|Canadian Warplane Heritage Museum}}<ref name=IGNlocations>{{cite news | author = Scott Chitwood | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/034/034940p1.html | title = X-Men's Sabretooth Scares Crap out of Kid, Toronto Set Visit, Wolvie Love Triangle, New Pics, & More | publisher = [[IGN.com|IGN.com]] | date = 2000-02-10 | accessdate = 2008-08-10 | archivedate = 2016-04-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160414130236/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/02/10/x-mens-sabretooth-scares-crap-out-of-kid-toronto-set-visit-wolvie-love-triangle-new-pics-more | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
電影於2000年7月12日在[[埃利斯島|埃利斯島]]首映<ref>"Ellis Island Premiere". ''X-Men 1.5'', Disk 2 (20th Century Fox Home Entertainment)</ref>，於埃利斯島上映2天後，《X戰警》在北美的3,025家劇院廣泛播映<ref name=open/>，澳洲則在7月23日上映，而其他多數國家都於8月發行<ref name=aus>{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/2000/film/news/x-traordinary-bow-1117783838/ |title=X-traordinary bow |access-date=2016-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301195605/http://variety.com/2000/film/news/x-traordinary-bow-1117783838/ |archive-date=2016-03-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[漫威工作室|漫威工作室]]藉著該部電影的成功，促進了許多漫威漫畫的改編電影（[[蜘蛛人_(電影)|蜘蛛人]]、[[驚奇4超人_(電影)|驚奇四超人]]、[[綠巨人浩克|綠巨人浩克]]及[[夜魔俠_(電影)|夜魔俠]]） <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/1999/voices/columns/marvel-takes-cue-from-its-superheroes-1117503960/ |title=Marvel takes cue from its superheroes |access-date=2016-11-01 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6UGSB6O4u?url=http://variety.com/1999/voices/columns/marvel-takes-cue-from-its-superheroes-1117503960/ |archive-date=2014-11-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 行銷 ===
2000年6月1日，漫威發行了一本漫畫書“X-Men：X-Men：Beginnings”，其中介紹了[[萬磁王|萬磁王]]、[[小淘氣|小淘氣]]及[[金鋼狼|金鋼狼]]的背景故事<ref>{{cite web | title = X-Men: Beginnings (Paperback) | publisher = [[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] | url = http://www.amazon.com/X-Men-Beginnings-Marvel-Comics/dp/0785107509 | accessdate = 2008-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070615050305/http://www.amazon.com/X-Men-Beginnings-Marvel-Comics/dp/0785107509 | archive-date = 2007-06-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，。

=== 原聲帶 ===
導演[[布萊恩·辛格|布萊恩·辛格]]原想聘請-{[[约翰·威廉姆斯|約翰·威廉姆斯]]}-來撰寫電影配樂，但由於與《{{link-en|下一個還是你|Urban Legends: Final Cut}}》時間安排的衝突，-{威廉姆斯}-拒絕了該提議<ref>{{cite news | author = Bill Ramey | title = Superman-on-Film | publisher = Batman-on-Film | date = 2006-02-12 | url = http://www.batman-on-film.com/supermanonfilm/article_singer_routh_wondercon2006.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081013024143/http://www.batman-on-film.com/supermanonfilm/article_singer_routh_wondercon2006.html | archivedate = 2008-10-13 | accessdate = 2007-05-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。辛格轉而請{{link-en|約翰·奧特曼|John Ottman}}作曲<ref>{{cite news | author = Marc Graser | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117503313.html | title = Ottman adds helming other duties | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1999-06-21 | accessdate = 2008-03-25}}</ref>。然而，一旦福斯從12月提前至7月發行電影，奧特曼對其他電影的作曲工作將與此衝突<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmscoremonthly.com/articles/2001/28_Feb---John_Ottman_Urban_Legends_Final_Cut.asp |title=John Ottman on Urban Legend: Final Cut |accessdate=2016-11-01 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310172827/http://www.filmscoremonthly.com/articles/2001/28_Feb---John_Ottman_Urban_Legends_Final_Cut.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終，辛格決定由[[邁克爾·凱曼|邁克爾·凱曼]]為電影製作配樂。

